<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>افزع لجوف قد أتتك خبطا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>انظر قافية <span class="c2">«اختلطا»</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
